items.example:
For 'table', it is a MaxCompute language to generate the metric, e.g., select count(*) as cnt from nni_test1_${exp_id}_${trial_id};
For 'summary', it is path of the summary file, e.g., oss://test-nni/examples/search/pai/metric/metric_${exp_id}_${trial_id}/
for 'stdout', it refers to the command to get the metric, e.g., cmd1

